text.section:
Upon application, nonpaying accounts shall be established for:
State police, local police, and fire department vehicles while the vehicles are being operated in an official capacity on a turnpike project;
Emergency vehicles operated by an ambulance service while the vehicles are being operated in an official capacity, in both emergency and nonemergency situations on a turnpike project;
Funeral processions on turnpike projects; and
School district vehicles while the vehicles are being operated in an official capacity on turnpike projects.
